name: APAC-GCP-VPN-TUNNEL-1
description: Primary IPSec tunnel - APAC OnPrem to GCP
comments: HA VPN tunnel 1. Routes traffic between APAC-DC-ONPREM and GCP VPC. AES-256-GCM encryption with SHA256 authentication. IKEv2 with DH Group 14.

name: APAC-GCP-VPN-TUNNEL-2
description: Secondary IPSec tunnel - APAC OnPrem to GCP (redundant)
comments: HA VPN tunnel 2. Provides redundancy for tunnel 1. AES-256-GCM encryption with SHA256 authentication. IKEv2 with DH Group 14.
